# realtime-multiplayer

## Core Functionality

The real-time multiplayer system implements three primary features:

1. Catch Broadcasting
- Notifies all connected players when fish are caught
- Shares catch details including weight and species
- Updates global leaderboards in real-time

2. Player Synchronization
- Maintains active player roster
- Updates player locations and activities
- Syncs achievement notifications

3. Chat System
- Global chat for all players
- Tournament-specific chat channels
- Location-based player communication

